dent Danielle Emerton of the has reassured people the show is still safe and asked for the public's help to find others involved in the stabbing. She said: \"We know that there were thousands of people at the show last night and we know that there's a lot of vision that is out there,\" urging anyone with information about the incident to come forward."}
